1
00:00:09,520 --> 00:00:13,758
=Miss The Dragon=

2
00:00:34,479 --> 00:00:36,520
Puteri Liu Ying, jangan lari!

3
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,240
Awak tunggu saya
di dalam kereta kuda dulu.

4
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,759
Saya akan pergi sekejap lagi.

5
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:51,040
Ya.

6
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:16,599
Kelip-kelip, di manakah tuan awak?

7
00:02:13,639 --> 00:02:14,960
Kenapa awak baru saja datang?

8
00:02:36,332 --> 00:02:38,980
♪Adakah penjelmaan semula
selama ribuan tahun♪

9
00:02:38,988 --> 00:02:42,640
♪Hanya untuk mencari awak?♪

10
00:02:43,793 --> 00:02:45,019
♪Segala fasa bulan♪

11
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:49,400
♪Seakan-akan hanya demi awak♪

12
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:53,501
♪Ikatan duniawi ibarat hujan bunga♪

13
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:57,840
♪Yang layu dan lenyap di depan ain♪

14
00:02:58,080 --> 00:03:02,800
♪Pungut sebutir air mata awak
dengan sekelip mata♪

15
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:07,376
♪Jika riak air Sungai Lethe
mengikut kemahuan saya♪

16
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,559
Turunkan saya!

17
00:03:13,679 --> 00:03:15,759
Raja Naga dalam cerpen akan melindungi
orang yang dicintainya.

18
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:17,360
Saya akan melindungi awak juga.

19
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,520
Baik.

20
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:21,520
Adakah awak masih takut sekarang?

21
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:23,000
Sepertinya...

22
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:26,559
Sepertinya saya sudah
tak begitu takut lagi.

23
00:03:27,839 --> 00:03:29,199
Saya akan melindungi awak selamanya.

24
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,399
Percayai saya,

25
00:03:30,639 --> 00:03:31,479
boleh?

26
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:33,360
Boleh.

27
00:03:33,423 --> 00:03:35,623
♪Hayat silam, sekarang dan kelak♪

28
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:37,759
Saya dah faham.

29
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:39,479
Balas jasa bermaksud berkahwin.

30
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,399
(Memandangkan kita dah kahwin,)

31
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,880
sudah tentu saya takkan
berubah selama-lamanya.

32
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:46,320
Awaklah Kelip-kelip saya
buat selama-lamanya.

33
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:51,080
Memandangkan nama awak Liu Ying,
[*Liu Ying bermaksud kelip-kelip]

34
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,080
apa kata saya memberi awak
kelip-kelip Berterbangan?

35
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:59,560
♪Tidak berpisah dengan awak lagi
selamanya dalam hayat kelak♪

36
00:03:59,679 --> 00:04:00,639
Kelip-kelip,

37
00:04:01,559 --> 00:04:02,440
saya suka awak.

38
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,559
Memandangkan kita saling menyukai

39
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,279
dan berjanji untuk bersama seumur hidup,

40
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,880
maka kita pasti boleh berkahwin.

41
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,360
Saya benar-benar berada di atas langit.

42
00:04:16,239 --> 00:04:18,920
Awak membawa saya terbang melalui awan.

43
00:04:19,359 --> 00:04:20,880
Ini sama seperti bayangan saya.

44
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,279
Awak pernah membayangkan?

45
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:24,399
Ya, saya pernah.

46
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:26,160
Pegang baik-baik.

47
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,119
Baik!

48
00:04:30,884 --> 00:04:33,620
♪Ikatan duniawi ibarat kelip-kelip♪

49
00:04:34,562 --> 00:04:37,620
♪Ketenangan di depan ain♪

50
00:04:38,078 --> 00:04:42,359
♪Jalan siapa yang diterangi, ia
terang seperti malam yang penuh bintang♪

51
00:04:42,359 --> 00:04:43,480
Cantik sekali.

52
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,320
Awak seorang panglima sekarang,

53
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,359
tetapi awak masih suka benda sebegini.

54
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:49,239
Saya suka bunga gugur berwarna-warni,

55
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:51,399
kelip-kelip yang berterbangan

56
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,399
dan juga bunga api ini.

57
00:04:53,427 --> 00:04:58,160
♪Kilauan cahaya pada telapak tangan
ialah bayang dalam mata siapa?♪

58
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:01,320
♪Menoleh sekilas ke belakang
lalu pergi dengan keberatan♪

59
00:05:04,359 --> 00:05:05,399
Liu Ying.

60
00:05:06,119 --> 00:05:07,040
Ayu.

61
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:08,359
Chenyue.

62
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:09,880
Rupa-rupanya,

63
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:12,119
awak berada di sisi saya selama ini.

64
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,440
Tak kira siapa awak,

65
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:16,880
saya akan berada di sisi awak selamanya.

66
00:05:20,679 --> 00:05:23,160
Ke mana kita akan pergi sekarang?

67
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,160
Kita akan pergi melihat tempat
yang cantik dalam mimpi awak itu.

68
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:27,880
Jangan takut.

69
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,959
Saya ada di sini.

70
00:05:30,135 --> 00:05:34,700
♪Percintaan ini berhenti
berkelana dalam hati demi awak♪

71
00:05:35,041 --> 00:05:41,380
♪Semoga hidup bersama awak
sepanjang hayat ini♪

